subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Frank Lickliter II shot his second consecutive 10-under 62 at Orange County National to take a nine-stroke lead after the second of six rounds in the PGA Tour National Qualifying Tournament in Winter Garden, Fla. The top 25 finishers and ties will earn 2008 PGA Tour cards, and the next number of players nearest 50 will receive full Nationwide Tour exemptions. The remaining players in the 166-man field will have conditional Nationwide Tour status.
